➜湖北诗人木子：蝶恋花·秋悟（外一首）
http://www.sohu.com/a/418374421_100115135	48720
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20200914/8512eba1062d405bb1b342b30402109a.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>蝶恋花·秋悟</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>文/木子</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">短暂人生终是梦，</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">苦乐悲欢，</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">风雨谁能共?</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">定律江山天摆弄，</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">心怀善念禅心种。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>教子言传儿女奉，</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>人在江湖，</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>德厚知恩重。</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>贪念无需皆有控，</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>逍遥尘世诗花颂。</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20200914/f9abfd95604f49d294cb04dbc8004e32.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>            <div class="lookall-box">
